<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10109737>
    dc:description "FIGURE 11. Torodora planusa sp. nov. and female genitalia which cannot be attributed to any of the known species: A, adult of T. planusa, holotype; B, labial palpus, lateral view; C, male genitalia, holotype, gen. slide no. CIS-7240/Park; D, ditto, aedeagus. Female genitalia of undetermined species: E, gen. slide no. CIS-7136/Park; F, gen. slide no. CIS-7160/Park; G, gen. slide no. CIS-7238/Park." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10109737/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10109745>
    dc:description "FIGURE 15. Dichomeris schoutedeniella (Ghesquière): A, adult, holotype; B, close-up head with antenna; C & D, labels; E, female genitalia, holotype, gen. slide no. CIS-7241/Park; F, close-up of the sac connecting with corpus bursae." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10109745/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

